WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:05.066
Hey, Shengsheng, you are back.

2
00:00:05.566 --> 00:00:06.600
Why are you here?

3
00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:08.900
Didn't I say don't come to me again?

4
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.600
I think it's cold now.

5
00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.266
Does this hotel have heating?

6
00:00:12.566 --> 00:00:14.333
I have prepared a silk quilt for you

7
00:00:14.333 --> 00:00:16.400
Cover it at night, don't freeze and catch a cold

8
00:00:17.133 --> 00:00:18.066
No.

9
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.166
I'm not as affectionate as you rich people

10
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:23.666
Hey, that's not what I meant.

11
00:00:23.733 --> 00:00:25.033
Look at these gifts

12
00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:26.933
This is my mom growing up.

13
00:00:26.933 --> 00:00:28.200
Gift for you

14
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:29.433
Take a look.

15
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:32.633
Enough I don't need your concern

16
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.966
I just want to live alone now

17
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:38.366
Shengsheng don't call me Shengsheng

18
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:39.433
I'll tell you what.

19
00:00:39.533 --> 00:00:40.633
My name is Tian Weiwei

20
00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:45.366
What's wrong with you on your birthday?

21
00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:46.633
Don't worry about it.

22
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.100
Don't show up in this hotel again

23
00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:50.166
Or I'll move

24
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:51.200
Until you find

